StepMania Note Package¶

class reamber.sm.lists.SMNotePkg.SMNotePkg¶
class reamber.sm.lists.SMNotePkg.SMNotePkg(dataDict: Dict[str, SMNoteList])
class reamber.sm.lists.SMNotePkg.SMNotePkg(hits: SMHitList, holds: SMHoldList, rolls: SMRollList, mines: SMMineList, lifts: SMLiftList, fakes: SMFakeList, keySounds: SMKeySoundList)

Bases: reamber.base.lists.NotePkg.NotePkg

This package holds hits, holds, rolls, mines, lifts, fakes, keySounds for each SMMapObj

__init__()¶
__init__(dataDict: Dict[str, SMNoteList])
__init__(hits: SMHitList, holds: SMHoldList, rolls: SMRollList, mines: SMMineList, lifts: SMLiftList, fakes: SMFakeList, keySounds: SMKeySoundList)

Initialize a package,

Can initialize with either overloaded method.

Parameters

  • dataDict – The data dictionary, it’ll be directly assigned to dataDict. The names must explicitly match

  • hits – The hits as a SMHitList

  • holds – The holds as a SMHoldList

  • rolls – The holds as a SMRollList

  • mines – The holds as a SMMineList

  • lifts – The holds as a SMLiftList

  • fakes – The holds as a SMFakeList

  • keySounds – The holds as a SMKeySoundList
